observations.recommendation:
We recommended to the Municipal Mayor to require the Municipal Accountant to:
Locate all the source documents and MOA with the source agencies to review the terms and conditions corresponding to the funds transferred in relation to the implementation of programs and projects;

Determine if the specific programs or projects for which the funds were transferred were already implemented, goods/services were already delivered, liquidation of funds were already submitted and received by the source agencies, and liabilities were already settled for proper adjustments in the books;

Return to the source agency any unused/unexpended balance if so stipulated in the MOA;

Request authority for the write off of dormant fund transfer accounts in accordance with COA Circular No. 2016-005 dated December 19, 2016, if warranted, duly supported by a quarterly aging of dormant fund transfers and other relevant documents.

