observations.recommendation:
We recommended to the Municipal Mayor and the local sanggunian to:
Craft ordinances and issue executive orders related to waste management and environmental protection;

Strengthen the current waste management system of the Municipality, including, garbage classification, collection, and recycling;

Add more waste recycling facilities; and

Focus on the recycling methods of the recyclables.

